  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AuthorPage
    Provides helper methods to perform actions on WCM author pages The classic UI uses /cf# in the url and the new AEM UI uses /editor.html with a suffix for the url
    DAMPage
    Provides helper methods to perform actions on DAM assets
    InboxPage
    Provides helper methods to perform actions on the inbox page
    LoginPage
    Provides helper methods to perform actions on the login page
    PublishPage
    Provides helper methods to perform actions on publish environment pages
    SiteAdminPage
    Provides helper methods to perform actions on the site admin page
    ToolsPage
    Provides helper methods to perform actions on the tools page
    WelcomePage
    Provides helper methods to perform actions on the welcome page
